<sn><md>#### Botany Exam Topics {.text-center}

* **Algae Identification**

  * Identify the given sample
  * Find the target algae
  * Identify the family
* **Slicing**: Identify the organ from the sliced specimen, draw its image, and label its parts
* **Disease**: Disease, Cause, and Agent; one will be given, and we have to determine the other two
</md></sn><sn><md>#### Template {.text-center}

