</md></sn><sn><md>##### Important {.fg-yellow}

* Everything must be written in pencil except **Date** and **Roll**.
* After identifying the algae or sliced specimen, call the teacher ("Mam") and write the species name with a pen. Then Mam will sign the paper, after which you can write the remaining details.
